stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_get_epoch: epoch = get_current_epoch(state)
    q_get_epoch --> q_get_max: max_blobs = get_blob_parameters(epoch).max_blobs_per_block
    q_get_max --> q_check_len: len(signed_beacon_block.message.body.blob_kzg_commitments) <= max_blobs
